                    <span>Keep your $'s. This is one of the worse books ever written. One star is way to much. You really can get better business advice from Tarrot cards. No substance and since it has been out a couple of years, history has proven his ideas flawed.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The worst book I ever read!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
